{"tid":2286564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侵侵團隊律師：賓州票站人員恐嚇GOP監票人","createTime":"2020-11-15T06:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T08:40:26.000Z","uid":144626,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a877887ce8e8d49e52c8ed34136d5b1e19f5d12a","tid":2286564,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"摘要：<br />\n1. 繼續屌左媒扮睇唔到舞弊<br />\n2. 有法庭手令都唔入得票站監票，當地副警察總長喺票站恐嘛佢，硬闖就會被捕<br />\n3. 之後當地選舉委員會更將佢列入黑名單，禁止入票站，原告變被告<br />\n4. 呢位律師更形容費城已經進入一黨專政年代<br />\n<br />\nCorey Lewandowski to Newsmax TV: Philly Engaged in Witness 'Intimidation'<br />\nLevying explosive claims of ballot witness intimidation by key Philadelphia officials, <span class=\"red\">Trump campaign senior adviser Corey Lewandowski on Newsmax TV rebuked the illegal actions of the &quot;tolerant left.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;I know we have the law on our side,&quot; Lewandowski told Saturday's &quot;Michelle Malkin: Sovereign Nation.&quot; &quot;<span class=\"red\">But many, many people who were there to witness the process, were intimidated and maligned and attacked and verbally assaulted.</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Look, that's the tolerant left as I call it, Michelle. As soon as you don't agree with them, all they want to do is attack you and physically harm you.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;You don't see that on the other side.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe board of elections supervisor, the sheriff of the county, and the deputy chief of police of the city of Philadelphia all threatened him, kept him from meaningful observation, and ultimately left him on a illegal do-not-enter list, Lewandowski said.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;All three summarily dismissed that court order, said that if I crossed the line that I would be arrested if I violated the rules &ndash; now, I had a court order,&quot; Lewandowski said.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The death threats and the threats of violence against me and the members of the team who are in Philadelphia &ndash; and candidly across the country &ndash; should never be tolerated,&quot; he continued.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;But, because they are a one-party rule in the city of Philadelphia, there's no recourse for that.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nLewandowski, author of &quot;Trump: America First: The President Succeeds Against All Odds,&quot; said there should have been &quot;nothing to hide.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It's shameful in this country &ndash; look, all we want is a free and fair and open election,&quot; Lewandowski concluded. &quot;All we want to do is be able to observe the counting of the ballots.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;If you have nothing to hide, why wouldn't you let us in to do that?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/intimidation-corey-lewandowski-philadelphia-legal-order/2020/11/14/id/997082/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsmax.com%2Fnewsmax-tv%2Fintimidation-corey-lewandowski-philadelphia-legal-order%2F2020%2F11%2F14%2Fid%2F997082%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=e43cc251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/intimidation-corey-lewandowski-philadelphia-legal-order/2020/11/14/id/997082/</a><br />\n<br />\nplus, 我之前講過Pilly DA好大官威，可以爬埋呢篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/philadelphia-da-threatens-trump-presidents-call-poll-watchers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fphiladelphia-da-threatens-trump-presidents-call-poll-watchers&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=4c7acd04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fphiladelphia-da-threatens-trump-presidents-call-poll-watchers&h=068fcbff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/philadelphia-da-threatens-trump-presidents-call-poll-watchers</a><br />\n<br />\n搞到咁，可唔可以要求費城選票無效或者重選？"},{"pid":"1c8887c7aedee119111d3b65bfe93b5b1d5695e5","tid":2286564,"uid":158404,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"左膠=CCP"},{"pid":"4882d01949d4cf70c8ee52df1aacbcd2f8f0d2f8","tid":2286564,"uid":127575,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"睇supreme court"},{"pid":"c210156cee95a968b9e7d7787847547b2bf0378a","tid":2286564,"uid":144626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"4882d01949d4cf70c8ee52df1aacbcd2f8f0d2f8","tid":2286564,"uid":127575,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"睇supreme court"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"最治本都係直接宣佈Pilly選票無效或者重選"},{"pid":"c66f998ddeadd1d2e11429797095bec39a374c7a","tid":2286564,"uid":60563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"cnn冇報<br />\nfake news<br />\nfact checked"},{"pid":"e4fcbe02c0dff70c71aca7e336f3ee8194f5d0ac","tid":2286564,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"離譜到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddbfcd6050154da17ee462f14a2b321cb750286","tid":2286564,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4fcbe02c0dff70c71aca7e336f3ee8194f5d0ac","tid":2286564,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"離譜到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"仲惡過元朗國"},{"pid":"4cb3583c7f5341756c74661f3557c0b8c2b80d71","tid":2286564,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g